{"tid":2369393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新娘潭路電單車越線高速過彎　收掣不及迎面硬撼私家車","createTime":"2021-01-17T05:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T15:13:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"16422214852581e812ac5560f3b592a46e10bf45","tid":2369393,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T05:59:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/191226174561957/videos/894157161392238\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F191226174561957%2Fvideos%2F894157161392238&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHLktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=bbcdb2fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/191226174561957/videos/894157161392238</a><br />\n<br />\n新娘潭路電單車越線過彎直撼私家車。網上流傳一段影片，顯示今早（17日）8時許，大埔新娘潭路一輛私家車沿沙頭角方向落斜行駛時，迎面一輛電單車越線高速過彎道上斜期間，疑未料到對面線有車，收掣不及直撼私家車。影片可見，橙色電單車撞向私家車前曾一度左右搖擺，紅衫司機其後被撞至直飛一旁，而電單車則倒臥地面，碎片滿佈一地，其後沿車道行駛的車輛均需慢駛避開。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，今早8時許一輛私家車及電單車於上址相撞，事件中一名電單車司機一度報稱手指受傷，但拒絕送院。"},{"pid":"d26447c5269433ee46e35d3da9ed9ae3e3e2ee9f","tid":2369393,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:00:23.000Z","msg":"又係新娘譚"},{"pid":"f40987308d2112d78429f83c25fda833b6d331d7","tid":2369393,"uid":13149,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:02:02.000Z","msg":"算大命 咁都死唔去"},{"pid":"8826212392d6ff025d4bcb5817e56a98af9b1e57","tid":2369393,"uid":76804,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:02:30.000Z","msg":"事件中一名電單車司機一度報稱手指受傷，但拒絕送院。<br />\n<br />\n之後唔好飲水呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a429b776a6d9bd0cb692f9b59577ef99e0cb9713","tid":2369393,"uid":41317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T06:03:03.000Z","msg":"好野喎<br />\n撞到咁都係整親手指"},{"pid":"7ebb79f99d29155c4a4b76a360af326d88c2a1c9","tid":2369393,"uid":50809,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"r